00:09:31.570 --> 00:09:33.220
TYLER PERRY: Well,
exactly right.

00:09:33.220 --> 00:09:34.390
But what it is for
me is like, there

00:09:34.390 --> 00:09:35.770
are a lot of people that
I've worked with that

00:09:35.770 --> 00:09:37.640
are first-timers, so
not just influencers,

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:40.090
but it's the first time
that they auditioned, did

00:09:40.090 --> 00:09:42.250
a great job, or they were like,
you know, I really want to act,

00:09:42.250 --> 00:09:42.610
can I?

00:09:42.610 --> 00:09:43.730
And I'll give them a shot.

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:46.127
So my studio and
what I've done, it's

00:09:46.127 --> 00:09:48.210
always been a training
ground for a lot of people.

00:09:48.210 --> 00:09:49.420
So I don't mind that.

00:09:49.420 --> 00:09:51.045
I don't mind being
in a situation where

00:09:51.045 --> 00:09:53.710
I can instruct and train, as
long as the right disciplines

00:09:53.710 --> 00:09:54.340
are there.

00:09:54.340 --> 00:09:58.180
If you're open to learning
and not just thinking,

00:09:58.180 --> 00:10:01.512
OK, this is just what it is, I'm
going to just do this my way.

00:10:01.512 --> 00:10:03.220
If you're not open to
learning, then it's

00:10:03.220 --> 00:10:03.920
going to be a problem.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:06.503
But everybody that I've worked
with has been open to learning,

00:10:06.503 --> 00:10:07.502
so yeah.

00:10:07.502 --> 00:10:08.710
Don't let them tell you that.

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:08.970
KEN WALKER: Yeah.

00:10:08.970 --> 00:10:10.990
TYLER PERRY: You tell them
you've been in a movie,

00:10:10.990 --> 00:10:11.840
you know what to do.

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.110
DE'ARRA TAYLOR: Oh
yeah, definitely.

00:10:12.110 --> 00:10:12.510
KEN WALKER: Right.

00:10:12.510 --> 00:10:12.720
TYLER PERRY: Yeah, yeah.

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:14.470
DE'ARRA TAYLOR: When people
ask who are you, I'm like,

00:10:14.470 --> 00:10:14.880
I'm an actor.

00:10:14.880 --> 00:10:15.710
TYLER PERRY: That's right.

00:10:15.710 --> 00:10:16.030
Own it.

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:16.530
Own it.

00:10:16.530 --> 00:10:17.210
That's right.

00:10:17.210 --> 00:10:19.120
KEN WALKER: So we want to talk
a little bit about your work

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:19.490
ethic.

00:10:19.490 --> 00:10:19.900
TYLER PERRY: Yeah.

