[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:10:57.100 --> 00:10:57.560
KEN WALKER: Yeah, LA.

00:10:57.560 --> 00:10:59.852
TYLER PERRY: Yeah, and I'm
not crazy, I'm not slipping.

00:10:59.852 --> 00:11:01.900
