00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:03.400
And listen, I'm on
stage some nights

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:04.580
and they have to give
me a note saying,

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:05.350
OK, this is where you are.

00:11:05.350 --> 00:11:07.490
Because it's like city
to city, place to place,

00:11:07.490 --> 00:11:10.420
and these arenas and theaters,
they all start to look alike.

00:11:10.420 --> 00:11:11.350
DE'ARRA TAYLOR: Always
working, that's good.

00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:12.250
TYLER PERRY: Well, work ethic.

00:11:12.250 --> 00:11:12.850
You were asking
about work ethic.

00:11:12.850 --> 00:11:14.130
KEN WALKER: Absolutely.

00:11:14.130 --> 00:11:16.047
Definitely want to know
where that comes from.

00:11:16.047 --> 00:11:17.680
Because as an influencer
or a YouTuber,

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:20.140
we see a lot of people reach
a certain level of success

00:11:20.140 --> 00:11:22.580
and kind of go stagnant,
becoming consistent,

00:11:22.580 --> 00:11:25.870
