trying to reach a certain goal.

00:11:25.870 --> 00:11:29.140
But you, it just seems like
with "Madea Family Funeral,"

00:11:29.140 --> 00:11:32.020
the tour, you just seem to
keep moving and keep moving.

00:11:32.020 --> 00:11:33.895
TYLER PERRY: Those people
aren't hungry, man.

00:11:33.895 --> 00:11:36.467
And when you're hungry, you
keep grinding, keep grinding,

00:11:36.467 --> 00:11:37.050
keep grinding.

00:11:37.050 --> 00:11:40.590
And it went from me wanting
to do well enough to take care

00:11:40.590 --> 00:11:43.240
of my mother to then realizing
that all of these people

00:11:43.240 --> 00:11:45.490
are depending on me,
to realizing that,

00:11:45.490 --> 00:11:48.150
wait, now you've got an
opportunity to lift and share

00:11:48.150 --> 00:11:49.400
and show other people the way.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:51.100
So I've always got a motivation.

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:53.350
As long as something's in
front of me, I'll work hard.

00:11:53.350 --> 00:11:54.730
But when you have
a four-year-old,

00:11:54.730 --> 00:11:55.772
he'll slow all that down.

