00:13:17.970 --> 00:13:19.030
TYLER PERRY:
Younger Madea, yeah.

00:13:19.030 --> 00:13:21.270
DE'ARRA TAYLOR: So one of you
guys could-- got it, noted.

00:13:21.270 --> 00:13:22.620
KEN WALKER: But you're still
